oh, I'll talk him into it.

00:34:51.040 --> 00:34:54.070
Or I'll negotiate my
point of view upon them.

00:34:54.070 --> 00:34:57.130
Artists-- and it might
be true by engineers.

00:34:57.130 --> 00:35:02.200
I don't know, but
artists do what

00:35:02.200 --> 00:35:04.960
they say in the
first few minutes,

00:35:04.960 --> 00:35:08.540
not what you tell them to.

